    Empatement de la police
    font-weight : bold -> font-semi-bold
  -->
  <p class="text-xl text-orange-800 bg-blue-200 p-1 m-1 ml-0 mt-10"> <span class="font-bold text-red-950">Hello</span> po lele lele</p>
